name: ElectricityCalculator
0:
”Alexa, start Electricity Calculator”
”Alexa, tell Electricity Calculator to convert 27 watts to amps.”
”Alexa, ask Electricity Calculator how many watts are in 23 amps?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: electricity calculator
des: Converts between watts and amps given the voltage (DC only). Watts and amps must be in whole positive numbers, and no fractions or decimals.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
